 common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":35,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"Robert FitzHerbert was born about 1420, in Derbyshire, England. He married Elizabeth Jocelyn about 1445. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in England."},"et":{"about 1420–":"umbes 1420–Surnud","1425–Female":"1425–Surnud","1445–1512":"1445–1512","1420–Male":"1420–Surnud","1425":"1425","1512":"1512","1445":"1445","1455":"1455","1420":"1420","about 1445":"umbes 1445","about 1420":"umbes 1420","Derbyshire, England":"Derbyshire, England","England":"England"},"fi":{"about 1420–":"noin 1420–Kuollut","1425–Female":"1425–Kuollut","1445–1512":"1445–1512","1420–Male":"1420–Kuollut","1425":"1425","1512":"1512","1445":"1445","1455":"1455","1420":"1420","about 1445":"noin 1445","about 1420":"noin 1420","Derbyshire, England":"Derbyshire, England","England":"England"},"fr":{"about 1420–":"environ 1420–Décédé","1425–Female":"1425–Décédée","1445–1512":"1445–1512","1420–Male":"1420–Décédé","1425":"1425","1512":"1512","1445":"1445","1455":"1455","1420":"1420","about 1445":"environ 1445","about 1420":"environ 1420","Derbyshire, England":"Derbyshire, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Robert FitzHerbert est né environ 1420, à Derbyshire, Angleterre. Il a épousé Elizabeth Jocelyn environ 1445. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé à Angleterre."}